---

<Fragment>
  <section class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center my-8 md:my-16">
    <div class="md:w-1/2 p-4 order-2 md:order-1">
      <p class="text-base text-secondary dark:text-blue-200 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">MEET YOUR COACH</p>
      <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2"> ðŸ‘‹ Hi there, I'm Izzy</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">I've been in your shoesâ€”struggling with endless resume rewrites and job applications that led nowhere.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">I'm a <strong>career zig-zagger</strong>, a <strong>jack-of-all-trades</strong> who loves learning new skills and diving into new industries. Telling a clear career story was tough, especially without well-defined performance metrics.</p>
