  </section>

  <section class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center my-8 md:my-16">
    <div class="md:w-1/2 p-4">
      <img src={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + 'assets/images/izzyprofilepic.webp'} alt="Colorful Image" class="w-full rounded-lg" />
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/2 p-4">
      <p class="mb-4">But my <strong>curiosity</strong> and <strong>love of learning</strong> prevailed. Talking to people revealed my unique industry insights, community-building skills, and partnership development experience.</p>
